OL,4,CNorwich: Open Academy criticised over
OL,5,Cbra and skirt advice to girls
OL,6, A secondary school has been criticised
OL,7, over "misogynistic and sexist" advice
OL,8, to female students on school uniform.
OL,10,FOpen Academy, Norwich, asked girls not
OL,11,Fto wear "very short skirts" or coloured
OL,12,Fbras to avoid receiving "unwanted
OL,13,Fcomments or attention".
OL,15,FOne parent said it perpetuated the idea
OL,16,Fthat girls were to blame for being
OL,17,Fsexually harassed, and an expert said
OL,18,Fthe advice was misogynistic and sexist.
OL,20,FThe school said there was "no excuse"
OL,21,Ffor "unwanted attention".
